  "This feeling will pass. You are not your rejection.",
  "Your nervous system is trying to protect you. Thank it, then guide it.",
  "Breathe in what you need. Release what no longer serves you.",
  "You are safe. You are worthy. You are enough.",
  "Sensitivity is your superpower, not your weakness.",
  "Between the trigger and the response, there is you.",
  "Every breath is a chance to come home to yourself."
